HEADWORD: Tergeminous
<hw>Ter*gem"i*nous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>tergeminus</ets>; <ets>ter</ets> thrice + <ets>geminus</ets>
doubled at birth, twin-born. Cf. <er>Trigeminous</er>.]</ety>
<def>Threefold; thrice-paired.</def> <rj><au>Blount.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
